# =============================================================================
# Sentry dashboard — Vite environment template
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Copy to `dashboard/.env.local` (which is gitignored by default in Vite) and
# fill in the slots below. ALL values here are PUBLIC because Vite inlines
# `VITE_*` vars into the client bundle at build time — never put secrets here.
#
# A fresh clone with NO `.env.local` boots fine: the dashboard falls back to
# the canonical NETWORKS[chainId] entries baked into src/lib/networks.ts, so
# you only need this file when overriding the defaults (forks, redeploys,
# registry address overrides, etc).
# =============================================================================

# --- SentryAgentRegistry address override ------------------------------------
# Optional override for the SentryAgentRegistry address. When unset, the
# dashboard reads `NETWORKS[chainId].registryAddress` (canonical Shannon
# deployment: 0x97F743A9AAa5AcAA73075C1B8F1921274755CF70). Only set this when
# running against a fork or a custom redeploy.
VITE_SENTRY_AGENT_REGISTRY=
